Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.44,main,,0,0,0,,To je bratr?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:08.32,main,,0,0,0,,Ano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.57,main,,0,0,0,,Náš bůh je s námi.
